## Gate B Objectives
<!-- Gate B confirms that the inception phase is complete: the solution is architected, the iteration plan is agreed, risks are understood, and the team is ready to begin structured discovery and delivery. -->

Gate B validates:
- Solution is defined at a sufficient level of detail
- Architecture key decisions have been made and documented
- Iteration plan covers all delivery phases with realistic timelines
- Risk and assumption registers are up to date
- Team is structured and ways of working are agreed

